</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A sellout crowd waited impatiently for an hour, then roared its approval as 
Barbra Streisand opened her first paid concert in 22 years with "Everything's 
as If We Never Said Goodbye." 
</P>
<P>
 "I'm a little nervous.Forgive me," she told the audience. 
