</P>
<P>
 * Records 
</P>
<P>
 Notre Dame 10-1 
</P>
<P>
 Texas A&M 10-1 
</P>
<P>
 * Rankings (AP) 
</P>
<P>
 Notre Dame -- No. 4 
</P>
<P>
 Texas A&M -- No. 7 
</P>
<P>
 * At Stake 
</P>
<P>
 Victories by Notre Dame and Florida State, and a loss by West Virginia would 
leave fickle pollsters with a dilemma --  
</P>
<P>
 whether to vote based on rankings or by head-to-head results. FIESTA BOWL 
Miami vs. Arizona 
</P>
<P>
 * Site 
