<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is New Year's Day. Among the agencies affected: 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: All post offices will be closed and no mail will be delivered. 
</P>
<P>
 * Banks: Most banks, savings and loan institutions and stock and commodity 
exchanges will be closed. 
</P>
