</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is New Year's Day. The following schedule will be in effect: * City, 
county and federal offices are closed. * County, state and federal courthouses 
are closed. * City and county libraries are closed. * Banks and savings and 
loans are closed. * Schools, colleges and universities are closed through Jan. 
2. * Mail: Post offices are closed. No mail delivery. * Trash: No service in 
most cities. * Buses: Limited service. * Parks: City- and county-run parks will 
be open. 
