<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Conservancy -- An article Thursday misstated the number of members on the 
board of the Santa Monica Mountains Conservancy. There are eight board members. 
</P>
